Text.Value: Luckily I'm not the type to hold someone's past against them. As long as I can trust you, I don't care what you are.
*You and Karlach haven't exactly earned each other's trust. Perhaps this isn't a good idea.*
The truth. Finally.
Change your mind.
Let's cross that bridge when we get to it. Only got room for so much drama at a time.

EditorData.NodeContext: A little annoyed but not too harsh

Text.Value: 'Happy' might be pushing it. But we make a formidable group. No sense breaking it up yet.
Tell her. She'll be glad you trusted her.
*Karlach seems practical enough. Perhaps she'll understand...*
If he lays a finger on you, I'll break it off. That's a promise.
Don't worry. I'll stomp him. Guaranteed.

EditorData.NodeContext: Matter of fact. Not doing it for Astarion but because she hates 'masters'

Text.Value: Anything else?
I'm glad you told me. Thought maybe you were going to keep it a secret forever.

EditorData.NodeContext: With a bit of an edge. She's a little miffed the player didn't tell her up front.

Text.Value: Risk it all and tell her anyway.
*You and Karlach have a certain rapport. She'll understand... won't she?*
What's on your mind?
We're good, right?
There it is. I was hoping you'd tell me yourself. I'm glad - very glad - you trusted me with this.
We're all a little complicated, aren't we? It's a bit of a race to the top of complication mountain, at this point.
Knew there was something off about you. That you might be a vamp entered my mind, for sure.
Well, it makes getting rid of the tadpole might be a little complicated for me.
I had my suspicions. Would've helped if you'd told me sooner. But it is what it is.

EditorData.NodeContext: With a bit of an edge. She's a little miffed the player didn't tell her up front.

Text.Value: Tell her the truth.
Well, my old master may come looking for me. He won't like that I've escaped his reach.
I didn't know for sure, of course. But between the fangs and the red eyes and the timeless wit, I had my inklings.
If you're happy to travel with me, I'm happy to travel with you.
You bet your arse I am.

EditorData.NodeContext: response to 'happy to travel with you'
